Class aldercroftGUImethods

  • java.lang.Object
    • aldercroft.aldercroftGUImethods

  • public class aldercroftGUImethods
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implement the functionality behind the aldercroftGUI.java interface. It also connects the GUI with the functionality of the DrawPanel.java.

    Franziska Blumenschein, Tobias Renner
